<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3872321>
    dc:description "FIG. 8. — Raphitoma pusaterii Prkić & Giannuzzi-Savelli n. sp., Mljet Island: A, holotype, MNHN-IM-2000-34889, h = 8.75 mm; B, paratype, coll. RGS 120247, h = 7.35 mm; C, paratype, coll. PRK, h = 9.2 mm; D, paratype, coll. PRK, h = 7.2 mm; E, paratype, coll. RGS 120248, h = 6.8 mm; F, coll. RGS, h = 5.8 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3872321/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3872323>
    dc:description "FIG. 9. — Raphitoma pusaterii Prkić & Giannuzzi-Savelli n. sp., Mljet Island (coll. RGS, h = 3.46 mm): frontal view of shell (A); apical (B), frontal (D) and dorsal (E) view of protoconch; detail of microgranules and transition from protoconch to teleoconch (C). Scale bars: A, 1 mm; B-E, 200 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3872323/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3872309>
    dc:description "FIG. 2. — Measurements taken on protoconch of Raphitoma pusaterii Prkić & Giannuzzi-Savelli n. sp.Diameter of nucleus (D nuc. = 105 µm), diameter of first half-whorl (D ½ = 159 µm), diameter of first whorl (D 1 = 190 µm), maximum diameter (Max. D = 440 µm), number of whorls (PW = 3.6), number of whorls of protoconch 1 (PW 1 = 1.1). Scale bar: 200 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3872309/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

